al theme in\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brave_New_World"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i1 Brave New World}}{\f0\fs24\b0 , to which Kaczynski refers in his text. Kaczynski's ideas of "}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Socialization#Oversocialization"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0 oversocialization}}{\f0\fs24\b0 " and "surrogate activities" recall\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sigmund_Freud"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0 Sigmund Freud}}{\f0\fs24\b0 's\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Civilization_and_Its_Discontents"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\i1 Civilization and Its Discontents}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~and its theories of\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rationalization_(psychology)"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0 rationalization}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~and\~}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sublimation_(psychology)"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0 sublimation}}{\f0\fs24\b0 \~(a term which Kaczynski uses three times to describe "surrogate activities").}{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Industrial_Society_and_Its_Future#cite_note-23"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0\super [}}{\f0\fs24\b0\ul\ulc0\super\cf4 23]}{ }
